name: Abnormal cellular immune system morphology
description: An abnormality of the morphology or counts of the cells that make up the immune system.

name: Abnormal leukocyte count
description: Number of leukocytes per volume of blood beyond normal limits.

name: Rectal abscess
description: A collection of pus in the area of the rectum.

name: Leukocytosis
description: An abnormal increase in the number of leukocytes in the blood.
